Switching to a different model later
1. Download the new model (see step 5 above for URLs).
2. Edit one line in the script:
bashsudo nano /var/lib/asterisk/agi-bin/transcribe_agi.py
Change MODEL_PATH at the top to the new folder name, e.g.:
pythonMODEL_PATH = "/opt/vosk-models/vosk-model-lv-0.1"
No restart needed — takes effect on the next call.

